About Us
Rentals
9am-4pm Daily Rentals
Chair: $9.99
Umbrella: $24.99
Umbrella & Two Chairs: $39.99 (+tax)
Bamboo Beach Bar
Our bamboo beach bar is set to fulfill all your drink cravings at exciting discounts. Featuring specialty drinks, non-alcoholic drinks, draft beers and more! Its always happy hour at the beach!
Amenities
Outdoor Showering Facilities, Bathrooms & Changing Areas, Volleyball,  Indoor Dining, Outdoor Gulf Front Dining, Tiki Bar, Lifeguards on Duty
Hershey’s Ice Cream
Our island ice-cream shop serves Edy's hand-dipped ice-cream. So when you're with us, enjoy the taste of original, delectable ice-cream!
Events
We host fun-filled, creative events on special occasions such as Thanksgiving & Christmas, as well as weekly live music and more, to make your day even more happier. Follow us on social media and stay updated about our upcoming events!
Gift Shop
We showcase large assortment of beach accessories, souvenirs and quality clothing at affordable prices. Browse our selection and buy something for your loved ones. Forgot something for you beach day? Don't worry, we have it here!
“I love this beach cafe..You can have breakfast, lunch or dinner all outside by the beach..All you can eat pancakes and their fish and chips are just perfect. ”
— Nancy L.  (Google Review)
Visit Us
We do not accept reservations. All guests are welcome on a first-come, first-serve basis.
4000 Gulf Drive
Holmes Beach, FL 34217
Hours
Monday–Sunday
Open: 8:00 am
Close: 7:00 pm
Phone
(941) 778-0784
